{"tid":1587993,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"唔理做咩都好 請保護自己","createTime":"2019-09-22T15:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T23:25:51.000Z","uid":241006,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"23b1f31a44c203ac3b2474766f2f09be09870abe","tid":1587993,"uid":241006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:46:04.000Z","msg":"首先前線手足無論做咩都好<br />\n我哋一班冷氣軍師都無條件支持<br />\n但請做足安全措施<br />\n包實啲自己<br />\n冇人地方先好換衫<br />\n留言有冇記者影住 特別cctvb<br />\n你哋係稀有資源 請特別小心<br />\n商場活動 都係<br />\n今日好多人口罩都冇個<br />\n俾人影晒<br />\n下次唔好啦<br />\n記得最好安全措施<br />\n咁樣俾人啦 好唔帶<br />\n得口罩已經好唔夠<br />\n連口罩都冇 我真係唔知點<br />\n唯有 燒衫 換鞋 剪髮<br />\n<br />\n總之 大家千祈要 小心 小心 小心"},{"pid":"cf4bedddaef630221acf7602fe9e207922ed3d76","tid":1587993,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"ddfb1dab880dbc39f99dd2fccf0ce4cbdb414391","tid":1587993,"uid":241006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:46:27.000Z","msg":"真係一個也不能少啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9196fdb1b309283b290e468d391d23c968f352d3","tid":1587993,"uid":241006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:47:11.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 1/10"},{"pid":"7d916a2d1cfada0dda18af84497b4d93bca4c7e6","tid":1587993,"uid":241006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:47:21.000Z","msg":"缺一不可 2/10"},{"pid":"985a888af0fc80689cf6dd6838d0553413ba42b9","tid":1587993,"uid":241006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:47:34.000